<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Db_Profiler::queryStart() takes the first 6 characters in the query string to determine which kind of query it is. This is unsafe because a query might for example start with a parenthesis.
Possible solution: check position of the words INSERT, DELETE, SELECT, and UPDATE. Whichever comes first decides what kind of query it is.</p>

